  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "\n<p><b>Type:</b> Ninjutsu (Medical)</p>\n<p><b>Rank:</b> 12</p>\n<p><b>Chakra Cost:</b> 12</p>\n\n<p><b>Learn DC:</b> 28 | <b>Successes:</b> 5</p>\n<p><b>Perform:</b> 16 | <b>Perform DC:</b> 32</p>\n\n<p><b>Components:</b> C, F, H</p>\n\n<hr>\n\n<p>You hold a severed limb where it should be, reattaching it to its original owner as long as it was severed no more than a day ago. For 30 days, -1 per level of the target and -1 per level of Medical Specialist and Exarch you have (minimum 1 day), the limb will not function correctly as it heals, causing the target to suffer a -4 penalty to attack and damage rolls, as well as to skill and ability checks.<br><br>In addition, they suffer a -4 penalty to their skill threshold and perform checks for any technique requiring hand seals or half seals. Furthermore, the target cannot run or charge if the reattached limb was a leg, and any encumbrance penalties it may suffer from are doubled if the reattached limb was an arm.</p>\n\n\n\n",
      "summary": "",
      "instructions": ""
    },
